OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start for most but
OL,6,Fgradually turning cloudier from the
OL,7,Fwest with some patchy rain. The best
OL,8,Fof the brightness across the east with
OL,9,Fsome sunny spells. Temperatures a
OL,10,Flittle closer to average for many.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain will continue to clear
OL,13,Feastwards overnight. Likely persisting
OL,14,Facross east and southeast England and
OL,15,Fthe Northern Isles by dawn. Skies
OL,16,Fclearing elsewhere. Largely frost-free.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
