OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FUnsettled at times with
OL,6,Fshowers and longer spells of rain,
OL,7,Fthese may turn heavy. Plenty of
OL,8,Fbrighter interludes as well. Feeling
OL,9,Fwarmer than of late in any brighter
OL,10,Fbreaks.
